This is on Win XP with the latest checkout of trunk.  It seems the relative
module paths in local.build.properties are being converted to absolute paths
somewhere during the build.

I had a quick look at GenerateModuleList.java, the first snippet is the most
recent revision.  The only thing I see is no longer using getSourceDir() but I
don't know if this would cause the problem.

